{"tid":1868412,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"7Feb - 長沙灣WEST PARK次輪銷售推出10伙，最終錄得2宗成交","createTime":"2020-02-07T14:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T12:00:00.000Z","uid":62935,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2346884bece6167e9c2fd1bdbbbb5cbf91fe813d","tid":1868412,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"興勝項目管理董事周嘉峯表示，旗下長沙灣WEST PARK周五(7日)進行次輪銷售推出10伙，最終錄得2宗成交，當中包括15樓A室，實用面積339方呎，成交價712.7萬元，呎價21,024元，創項目新高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他指出，該盤至今累沽12個單位，扣除優惠套現約7,740萬元，平均呎價約1.92萬元。<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然最近新型肺炎疫情有擴大迹象，但項目屬市區少有中細價供應，不擔心銷情會受太大影響。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e71eb988ad6c681ac08e8f899940b443acfb016","tid":1868412,"uid":62935,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"全盤 63伙<br />\n成功售出12伙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔太擔心！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a774233ccf7406973dd5775a91cce2d349d4875","tid":1868412,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"呢個價點解唔買港灣豪庭? 得63伙, 管理費應該好貴"},{"pid":"efbffd1d3c39a2855b698cb1e916efcc793f068c","tid":1868412,"uid":62935,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6a774233ccf7406973dd5775a91cce2d349d4875","tid":1868412,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"呢個價點解唔買港灣豪庭? 得63伙, 管理費應該好貴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"反而想知， 「剛需」點解唔去瘋搶？<br />\n6M 幾入門咋喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來「剛需」都睇市況？<br />\n咁咩叫剛需？唔「剛」的「需」又叫唔叫剛需？<br />\n點解唔就咁叫需求？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi